OL,3,CLeicestershire man given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'sceptical' of government
OL,5,Csupport scheme
OL,7,FA man from Leicestershire who was
OL,8,Fgiven infected blood has said he's
OL,9,Fstill "sceptical" of the government's
OL,10,Fplan to compensate victims.
OL,12,FIt comes as the government said
OL,13,Fvictims of the infected blood scandal
OL,14,Fwill receive financial support for
OL,15,Flife from the end of this year.
OL,17,FSuresh Vaghela was 20 when he was told
OL,18,Fhe had HIV during a phone call in 1983.
OL,20,FHe was a haemophiliac and had been
OL,21,Fgiven infected blood.
