OL,3,CLeicestershire man given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'sceptical' of government
OL,5,Csupport scheme
OL,7,FHe said: "The government have promised
OL,8,Fso many things in the past and never
OL,9,Factually delivered.
OL,11,F"The words have been hollow in the
OL,12,Fpast so we think they're hollow now.
OL,14,F"The government keep saying it's going
OL,15,Fto be life-changing amounts of money
OL,16,Fbut it isn't.
OL,18,F"It'll be life-assisting because it'll
OL,19,Fhelp us but life-changing is what they
OL,20,Fgave us.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
