OL,3,CLeicestershire man given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'sceptical' of government
OL,5,Csupport scheme
OL,7,F"(Infected blood) changed our lives;
OL,8,Fwe couldn't be who we were or lead the
OL,9,Flives we were living.
OL,11,F"Until they show action I'm a bit
OL,12,Fsceptical."
OL,14,FHis brother Praful died in 1995 from
OL,15,FAIDS. In the year that followed Suresh
OL,16,Fwent to 70 funerals as many of his
OL,17,Ffriends were infected with
OL,18,Fcontaminated blood.
