OL,4,Cblood 'sceptical' of government
OL,5,Csupport scheme
OL,7,FSuresh, who grew up in Coventry, was
OL,8,Ftold by his doctor to go home, tell
OL,9,Fhis family and get his paperwork in
OL,10,Forder as he only had two or three
OL,11,Fmonths to live.
OL,13,FHe said he was given no information or
OL,14,Fsupport, and was told not to tell
OL,15,Fanyone about his diagnosis.
OL,17,FIn 2005, Suresh found out he was one
OL,18,Fof more than 800 people who had also
OL,19,Fbeen infected with Variant
OL,20,FCreutzfeldt`Jakob disease (vCJD), an
OL,21,Fincurable brain disease.
