OL,5,Csupport scheme
OL,7,FMore than 30,000 people in the UK were
OL,8,Finfected with diseases linked to
OL,9,Fcontaminated blood they received
OL,10,Fduring the 1970s and 1980s.
OL,12,FThe government's announcement comes
OL,13,Fmonths after a seven-year public
OL,14,Finquiry published its final report
OL,15,Finto what it called the "biggest
OL,16,Ftreatment disaster in NHS history."
OL,18,FVictims who were used for research
OL,19,Fwithout their knowledge will be
OL,20,Feligible for an extra #10,000.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
