OL,5,Csupport scheme
OL,7,FSome will also be given an increased
OL,8,F"social impact" award which recognises
OL,9,Fthe stigma and isolation victims have
OL,10,Fsuffered.
OL,12,FInfected people will start receiving
OL,13,Fpayments through the new framework by
OL,14,Fthe end of the year.
OL,16,FPaymaster General and minister for the
OL,17,FCabinet Office Nick Thomas-Symonds
OL,18,Fsaid: "This is an important milestone
OL,19,Ffor victims and campaigners who have
OL,20,Fwaited far too long for justice.
